rc=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係有冇錢問題，成件事根本就好簡單快捷</blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>一入spareroom<br />\n人地specify左要professional，揀都唔使揀啦，仲比唔比你租</blockquote>屌<br />\n講到咁大口氣原來係shared house<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我睇完個reply就知根本不用理會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有人睇樓要睇好耐，可能有唔同既要求（有寵物／要有車位etc）<br />\n有人agent覆得快，有人agent覆得慢<br />\n有人好快就租到<br />\n個個人既情況都唔同，唔好下下用自己果套一野就度落人地個情況度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我覺得呢度巴絲打大家都係想分享自己既經驗，等其他人有個basic個concept可以了解下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n更何況明明樓上講緊係租樓，唔係租房<br />\n佢將兩樣野撈埋一齊黎講，我夠知租房易d啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望有追post／想加入9up既朋友可以搞清楚個狀況先加入討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70ab50866a2940b2f97906b362fdec7cd43974a5","tid":2510674,"uid":362331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0a0efb61d0900199acb85833835d13ffe929b67","tid":2510674,"uid":17359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T10:22:56.000Z","msg":"是<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T10:24:34.000Z","msg":"Thx bro，希望一切順利啦😞<br />\n睇黎你個host都慣慢慢黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n話咁快就13 各位同路人順順利利啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22593be488424beca27594b53432582c26d666d0","tid":2510674,"uid":17359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid"